Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.api

Class KernelTransactionImplementationHandle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.api.KernelTransactionImplementationHandle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KernelTransactionHandle
    class KernelTransactionImplementationHandle
extends Object
implements KernelTransactionHandle
    A KernelTransactionHandle that wraps the given KernelTransactionImplementation. This handle knows that KernelTransactionImplementations can be reused and represents a single logical transaction. This means that methods like markForTermination(Status) can only terminate running transaction this handle was created for.
